    pharmacologyFocus: "moa,receptor_activity,adverse_effects,drug_interactions",
    bennerBreakdown: "Expert MRSA management requires understanding that ceftaroline doesn't bypass PBP2a — it BINDS it with high affinity due to structural modifications. This distinction (overcoming vs. bypassing resistance) is fundamental to antimicrobial pharmacology."
